    <fr:title text="Positively generated dcpos › "><fr:link href="jms-0023.xml" title="Positively generated dcpos" addr="jms-0023" type="local">Positively generated dcpos</fr:link> › </fr:title>
    <fr:taxon>Proof</fr:taxon>
  </fr:frontmatter>
  <fr:mainmatter>
  <fr:p>(2) implies (1) by setting <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[I = {\mathopen {}\left \{a\right \}\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex>. Conversely, assume that each element is the supremum of its positive part and fix a semidirected subset <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[I\subseteq  A]]></fr:tex>. We compute:</fr:p>

  <fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[\bigsqcup {\mathopen {}\left \{a \in  I \mid  \mathsf {pos}\,a\right \}\mathclose {}}
  =
  \bigsqcup _{a\in  {\mathopen {}\left \{a \in  I\mid  \mathsf {pos}\,a\right \}\mathclose {}}}a
  =
  \bigsqcup _{a\in  I}\bigsqcup _{p\in  \mathsf {pos}\,a} a
  =
  \bigsqcup _{a\in  I} a
  ]]></fr:tex>
</fr:mainmatter>
